Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里贝斯的生态脉冲正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是正常值
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的地方也看不出什么异常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说我没问题咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里贝斯变成像你这样的形态还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也不敢断言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过视野全黑会不会是前次战斗时留下的伤造成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在的状况来看虽然没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以防万一我们在你右手安装了测量生态脉冲的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会有异常的感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就能时刻掌握你生态脉冲的变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么担心也没用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还保有回忆么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水和生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是这次自由研究的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究结果预定于下周发表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天各个组就讨论研究发表的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有每个组的组长今天也要选举出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 水和生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到水的话应该就是海啦河啦什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湖！我去过摩周湖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩周湖和生活？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么研究啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和生活的话应该是下水道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么给人感觉很无聊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就研究雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我觉得还是研究雪更好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也算是水？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 雪和冰也算水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这个问题问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪和冰是水的其他形态所以也都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过必须要考虑到它们化成水的时候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不如研究洪水怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洪水？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 之前电视里也放过的洪水灾害特别节目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说以前的人们为了保护家园防范洪水做了很多努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的哦 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真的很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那很酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很酷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是水和人类的战斗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很象电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就研究这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道把那个节目录下来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我本来以为可以就这么发表了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢？那样还怎么能算是自由研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么谁来做组长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是小光做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你提出要研究洪水的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该是最了解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说的话小翼也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不来组长的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得小光做好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这么决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 爸爸要开店了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这个牧场的店要开2号分店了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在托朋友帮我找开店的地段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定春天的时候我们就可以回到东京了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2号店要开在东京吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好不容易才习惯了这里的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 爸爸的梦想好不容易才能实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来一定要和飞鸟她们分开了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很替爸爸高兴 不过还是会觉得有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是只要小光在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有小光在寂寞点也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是小光不在的话我真不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我能不能回原来的学校了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是友子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要是能再见到友子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么介绍我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里做的事再做一次不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光是我分居的双胞胎妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了东京的学校要是还能和小光一个班级就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要离开这里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须要和小翼一起去的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会考虑你们以后的交通工具的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们剩下的时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事你自己也应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的事结束后你必须和我们一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到母体玛基并处理掉它之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就要和小翼分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天必须要和小翼分开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:09:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是小光不在的话我真不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸 我们走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖在家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午爸爸要和新先生去办2号店的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为可能会比较晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的晚饭你们去茨城家吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经和京子打过招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 爸爸会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 我们来比谁先跑到车站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 跑那么快很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真顽皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我说几次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化部的记者写这种生物论文式的报道有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是非常严重的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得尽早发表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说枯萎现象的原因是进化的病毒巴浦特利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那个叫什么巴浦特利亚的病毒\N是随着从宇宙落下的陨石来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经考虑的很周全了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在进一步核实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要说的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:10:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是告诉过你我们的报纸没有栏目可以刊登这个报道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑田 你到底有没有搞清楚自己的立场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西去科学杂志或者植物研究杂志上发表吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要去镇上的图书馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 或许能找到和自由研究有关的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大家一起去图书馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去那边看这本书了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那我们分开找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从理科的书架找 小翼从社会科的书架找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先分开挑书 待会儿一起看不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样比较快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞鸟 看到小光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是和你在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没来我们这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是去了别的书架找书了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里？我去了一趟厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小翼已经选好书了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也得快点了 等我一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也要烤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点进来坐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做在淳志和亮的中间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼也快点来坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤肉要从蔬菜开始吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要吃好多蔬菜再吃烤肉才是北海道流的吃法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样配上就能吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有肉有肉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么只吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁说要从蔬菜开始吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过那话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人不用管这些的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs28}（这块肉归我了）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 你们要搬到东京的哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道是不是要搬到东京呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs28}（再来一碗 一大碗）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟朋友们说了要搬家的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟飞鸟和典子说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我高中毕业以后一定要去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天吃烤肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京子 总是麻烦你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么的 人多了才热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光坐在淳志和亮的中间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 让他们帮忙烧烤就总是烤肉给我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也烤了很多蔬菜的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都交给你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别笑成那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里在加深点怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这边就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下堂课就要发表了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个组都要好好准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们之间是不是有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是日记还没写完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来写
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该还追得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天有事 要坐公交车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你要回东京了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次你和唐泽她们说的时候我听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的有事才乘公交车的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一站持田医院前站
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田医院前站
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 下一站停车
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茨原
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的事 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开车了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看什么呢 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来啦 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.18,0:24:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气预报还说晚上会停的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.56,0:24:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.94,0:24:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光是不是在生我的气？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.92,0:24:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得你在回避我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.59,0:24:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.47,0:24:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.22,0:24:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也会分开的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.18,0:24:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是很正常的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.68,0:25:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼也会和我以外的人说话、玩耍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.98,0:25:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.69,0:25:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且老是只和我一起也会很无聊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.36,0:25:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.45,0:25:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.70,0:25:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光不是说过会一直和我在一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.79,0:25:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和小光在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.83,0:25:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然也想和小翼在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.25,0:25:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.46,0:25:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得小翼和其他的朋友聊天也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.06,0:25:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.60,0:25:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来练习明天的发表内容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.15,0:25:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.86,0:25:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.80,0:26:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光肯定是在回避我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.61,0:26:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他的朋友聊天也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.82,0:26:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.83,0:26:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要是小光不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.50,0:26:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.05,0:26:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光要走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.34,0:26:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一只玛基被消灭了的话就要和DD他们...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.81,0:27:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.15,0:27:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.57,0:27:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才一直回避我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.91,0:27:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.08,0:27:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.05,0:27:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.38,0:27:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要...和小光分开
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.44,0:28:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...发大水人们就到高地上的神社去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.74,0:28:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.29,0:28:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.29,0:28:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们为了保护家园不受洪水灾害做了很多努力
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.59,0:28:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行着改道河流...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.13,0:28:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后人们就建造了排水管道和渠道\N可以一直为暖房提供用水
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.23,0:28:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就可以使用农耕器械来插秧和收割
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.82,0:28:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排水设施良好的高地也可以用来作为耕地
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.24,0:28:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了冬天就可以成为塑料大棚进行温室栽培
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.12,0:28:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也可以说是科学设备的发展的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.66,0:28:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发表完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.76,0:28:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.01,0:29:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么轮到下一组了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.89,0:29:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.03,0:29:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光的脉冲的数值在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.41,0:29:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.00,0:29:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.50,0:29:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.17,0:29:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 我觉得有点不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.76,0:29:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.09,0:29:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去保健室看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.84,0:29:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.68,0:29:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能走路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.64,0:29:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生的卫生委员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.68,0:29:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送小光去保健室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.44,0:29:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.61,0:29:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.48,0:29:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我还有事要拜托小翼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.78,0:30:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来代替我给我们组做发表
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.99,0:30:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.54,0:30:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.83,0:30:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起练习的你应该最清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.54,0:30:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.21,0:30:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先这么决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.09,0:30:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.26,0:30:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.09,0:30:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 你一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.55,0:30:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.01,0:30:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么木村同学 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.31,0:30:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.98,0:30:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么跳过椎名同学的小组先发表下面的一组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.24,0:30:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我先去看看她 你在这里继续观察
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.49,0:30:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.87,0:30:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低地一遇到暴雨就会大水沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.66,0:30:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挖出一部分的泥土堆积成温室种上稻子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.96,0:31:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是堀田的由来...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.98,0:31:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.61,0:31:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面轮到椎名这组发表了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.12,0:31:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.96,0:31:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始发表
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.92,0:31:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们4组的研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.72,0:31:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制洪水
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.39,0:31:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.81,0:31:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.70,0:32:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.91,0:32:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.80,0:32:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要换你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.11,0:32:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.82,0:32:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算小光不在也必须要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.75,0:33:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前一到发大水人们就到\N建在高低上的神社或寺庙里去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.09,0:33:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里人们为了保护家园不受洪水灾害做了很多努力
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.97,0:33:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行着改道河流的工程
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.31,0:33:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐埠县海津町的千本松原就是在那个工程中诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.82,0:33:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 恢复正常了？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.11,0:33:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.33,0:33:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经很正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.49,0:33:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.75,0:33:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外建造称作水屋的房子来控制洪水
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.71,0:33:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是水屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.63,0:33:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内部经过各种精心构造
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.13,0:33:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如上所见控制洪水是不能忽视、非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.06,0:33:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发表完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.35,0:34:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 做的很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.50,0:34:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.88,0:34:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.54,0:34:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.75,0:34:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.80,0:34:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.47,0:34:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.13,0:34:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.93,0:34:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究发表怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.14,0:34:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼表现的很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.52,0:34:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想让小光也看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.90,0:34:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？小翼真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.19,0:34:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过一开始我还真不知道该怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.03,0:34:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手和脚都不停地在抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.70,0:34:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 不过还是发挥得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.41,0:35:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且老师还表扬了你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.50,0:35:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.83,0:35:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家还热烈鼓掌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.92,0:35:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs28}（那时真的很紧张）
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.96,0:35:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.63,0:35:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枯萎的树林？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.67,0:35:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你在研究枯萎现象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.13,0:35:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我猜你会去调查的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.01,0:35:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.56,0:35:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我们剧组为了拍摄\N《已经失传了的祭奠系列》到了碳坑后面
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.15,0:35:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碳坑的后面？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.40,0:35:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那一带的树林大范围的枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.82,0:35:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我详细的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.66,0:35:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.87,0:35:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.79,0:35:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.08,0:35:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.34,0:35:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.42,0:35:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有话要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.80,0:36:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是你装了探测装置后收集的脉冲数据
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.69,0:36:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有一段时间显示是正常值 但是这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.73,0:36:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我就是这个时候眼前全部变黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.03,0:36:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.95,0:36:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这在一般的里贝斯特性里是不可能有的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.20,0:36:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有没有其他奇怪的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.41,0:36:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 现在很好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.42,0:36:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.71,0:36:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是上次受的伤是不是还留着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.97,0:36:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之还是先继续收集数据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.22,0:36:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.60,0:36:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.19,0:36:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.24,0:37:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是北狐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.50,0:37:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸是在追它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.13,0:37:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DD说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.21,0:37:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 他说一直在找玛基可总也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.64,0:37:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.23,0:37:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸 我们要回东京 要分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.69,0:37:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会记住天丸的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.03,0:37:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸也不要忘记我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.30,0:37:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.63,0:38:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.60,0:38:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一只玛基被消灭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.06,0:38:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一只玛基被消灭的话小光就要走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.74,0:38:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和DD他们一起回宇宙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.07,0:38:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.83,0:38:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才一直在回避我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.79,0:38:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让我可以适应没有小光的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.46,0:38:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 告诉我实话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.47,0:38:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.19,0:38:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.69,0:39:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我们消灭了所有的玛基就要回本星了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.49,0:39:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DD说我们不能总是留在这个星球的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.17,0:39:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 一直都在瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.22,0:39:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...我不想和小翼分开
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.65,0:39:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.90,0:39:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.62,0:39:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远记着小翼的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.33,0:39:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.28,0:40:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这前面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.54,0:40:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 得快点
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.28,0:41:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.93,0:41:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿的雪积的真少
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.94,0:41:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地面是热的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.69,0:41:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.86,0:42:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥林蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.82,0:42:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.24,0:42:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到本星后一定要把小光交给研究机关吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.83,0:42:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.33,0:42:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得可能回到本星时\N你能在小光的处理问题上做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.09,0:42:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.22,0:42:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.84,0:42:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.03,0:43:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.66,0:43:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是上次那只玛基出现的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.08,0:43:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.29,0:43:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 决不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.37,0:43:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只就是母体玛基！
